{"tid":2458953,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–配以紫外光種植生菜","createTime":"2021-03-24T00:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T05:53:16.000Z","uid":38861,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1572bf5de8466f45e69f7854dba38ad578fdd8d2","tid":2458953,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:31:01.000Z","msg":"植物的生長全賴光合作用提供能量及資源。在這層面上，所選用的光源亦是一大學問。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYb5rrq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYb5rrq.jpg&h=d3d01e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）葉綠素(Chlorophyll)為植物吸收光線的重要位置。<br />\n利用化學物分離葉綠素的話，共可分為葉綠素a及葉綠素b兩大部份。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTKOpc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTKOpc8.jpg&h=56421031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉綠素a主要吸收紅光，而葉綠素b則主要吸收藍光。<br />\n<br />\n綠光並沒有有效地被葉綠素吸收的關係，因此葉綠素在我們的眼中呈為綠色。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）近來有研究發現，配合日照再加上紫外線燈(UVA)的方式種植，生菜的葉綠素、蛋白質、維他命C及糖粉對比單獨日照方式種植更之為高，而硝酸鹽的成份則有所降低。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JTOvCyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJTOvCyb.jpg&h=e0201a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這有可能是紫外線對植物的新陳代謝產生變化所致，還需要進一步的研究才能證實。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97eL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=a87ebb1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97eL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=ec7afa67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0308814620325899?via%3Dihub#t0010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0308814620325899%3Fvia%253Dihub%23t0010&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97eL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=9f7ec499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0308814620325899?via%3Dihub#t0010</a>"},{"pid":"39a212907a5a880ad33be12d786d7d1f44142b27","tid":2458953,"uid":146092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432a8d9863d2f50fdc0a8999af4b2ce18fa4ddf9","tid":2458953,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d53af54fd96032501ddc9208326f190d7525bb7","tid":2458953,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:32:22.000Z","msg":"今日遲咗出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9965817a30e4d159e0570ecc154320b73fced2e5","tid":2458953,"uid":194690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:33:21.000Z","msg":"gchi"},{"pid":"f2389b547dbe86c06a59c26347f9ae3ec0fa76c9","tid":2458953,"uid":325023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00